      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Configuration\n\n- Credentials needed: Gemini (or any AI model API), YouTube OAuth2, Google Sheets OAuth2, Supadata API (Free 100 requests/month, no credit card needed).\n\n- Configure the trigger Google Sheet node so that it is connected to your spreadsheet with the following columns that include the YouTube video's ID & the status (either \"Waiting\" or \"Done\"):\n\n\"| youtube_id | analysis_status | linkedin_1 | linkedin_ 2 | linkedin_3 | reels_1 | ... | shorts_1 | ... |\"\n\nIf columns are not exact, you will have to reconfigure the rest of the nodes so it matches with your column's titles.\n\n- Edit each AI agent's user prompt input with your niche and background in detail (a space to fill in is provideed already)",
        "height": 480,
