      "parameters": {
        "content": "## How it works\n\n- Workflow triggers every minute (or your own specified time) and looks for youtube video IDs in your spreadsheet that has the status \"Waiting\" (must be exact).\n- It takes the video IDs with that status and uses the YouTube API to get the video's metadata + Supadata's API to get the video transcript.\n- Each AI agent analyzes the YouTube title and transcript to create platform-specific short-form content outlines and drafts, following proven and researched techniques for their platform.\n- The content outlines and drafts are then added into your Google Sheet's respective columns for each content.",
        "height": 480,
